 # This class is part of an EXPERIMENTAL API.
class HannahService:
    """============================================================
    Hannah gRPC Service

    Allows external services (Telegram bot, web UI, etc.) to:
    - query and manage the user registry
    - submit text commands and receive answers
    - trigger TTS announcements on satellites
    - inspect registered satellites
    - query live car state
    - subscribe to a stream of Hannah events (car parked, resident arrived, …)
    - register as a satellite audio proxy (Go gRPC proxy replaces UDP server)
    ============================================================

    """

